        <!-- What to Expect -->
        <article class="card">
          <div class="badge"><i></i>What to Expect</div>
          <h2>What You Can Expect</h2>
          <p>
            You will leave with clarity. What matters, what you are training, and how you will measure improvement. The goal is less noise and faster progress.
          </p>
          <div class="cols">
            <div class="mini"><b>Assess</b><span>Baseline skills and shot pattern. Identify what is costing you strokes.</span></div>
            <div class="mini"><b>Prioritize</b><span>Pick the top one or two priorities that will move scoring fastest.</span></div>
            <div class="mini"><b>Train</b><span>Drills and reps tied to ball flight and scoring. No random practice.</span></div>
            <div class="mini"><b>Transfer</b><span>On-course verification and adjustments so results show up when it matters.</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="actions">
            <a class="btn primary" href="contact.html">Start Here</a>
            <a class="btn" href="about.html">View Credentials</a>
